Conjuration (Healing)
Levels: Cleric 4, Druid 5, Paladin 4
Components: V, S
Range: Touch
Target: Creature touched.
Duration: Instantaneous

The energy of life flows through you, warming your hand - and indeed your very soul. You infuse this warmth into the wounds of your ally.

Roll a number of d4s equal to half your caster level + 10 (maximum 20d4). The result is the number of hit points of damage instantly healed.